The '''''Upright''''' was an [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] [[Warship/Legends|warship]] of unknown class that was present at the [[Battle of ThonBoka]]. Its [[Captain/Legends|captain]] questioned [[Rokur Gepta]]'s tactics before the main battle. The [[Sorcerers of Tund/Legends|Sorcerer of Tund]] subsequently ordered both the captain and his second in command thrown out an [[Airlock/Legends|airlock]] for being individualist.<ref name="Lando Calrissian and the Starcave of ThonBoka">''[[Lando Calrissian and the Starcave of ThonBoka]]''</ref>

